      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Exciting News! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Imagine this: Whenever a new subscription happens in chargify, we work our magic behind the scenes to ensure everything runs smoothly.</p>\n<p>Here’s how it goes down:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Step 1: Payment Success Verification<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/credit_card.png?v=12\" title=\":credit_card:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":credit_card:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Check if the payment is successful in Chargify. (Chargify module)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Step 2: Customer ID Retrieval<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/heavy_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":heavy_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":heavy_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Search for the customer ID in the Monday board. (<a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> module)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Step 3: Update Deal Stage<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bar_chart.png?v=12\" title=\":bar_chart:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bar_chart:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Update the deal stage column in Monday Board to “Active” to keep everyone informed. (<a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> module)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Step 4: Training Completion<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/spiral_calendar.png?v=12\" title=\":spiral_calendar:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":spiral_calendar:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Mark the Calendly training as completed in <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>. (<a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a> module)</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/link.png?v=12\" title=\":link:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":link:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> With this seamless integration, we’re streamlining our processes and staying organized like never before. No more manual updates or missed steps - just smooth sailing ahead! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sailboat.png?v=12\" title=\":sailboat:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sailboat:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Join us in celebrating this exciting milestone as we take our workflow to the next level with <a href=\"http://make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">make.com</a>, Chargify, and <a href=\"http://Monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Monday.com</a>! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/0/c061362f0bcdf406e453e7547a38dd9fb8bb5b52.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/0/c061362f0bcdf406e453e7547a38dd9fb8bb5b52.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"344\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">691×345 21.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p><strong>If you need any implementation support kindly contact us</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\nVisit us <a href=\"https://www.msquare.pro/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">here</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCqidlIIwbejxZmRUWBICcjQ\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Youtube Channel</a></p>"
